We are running into an issue where users in a space are receiving approval request for restricted pages.  Just because a user last edited the page and has admin/restrict permissions shouldn’t give them the authority grant access to restricted pages.  We have sensitive information stored on some of our restricted pages and we need to strictly control who fields requests for access and who grants access to those pages.
We would like to see the ability to grant access to restricted pages as a separate permission in the space.
We feel that the ability to grant access to a restricted page should be a separate permission such as “grant restriction”.  This permission should appear as checkbox along with all the other page permissions for the space.

